<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>LumenNyx Studios – Private Model Portal</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Private model & staff portal for LumenNyx Studios, an independent adult production studio based near Wallkill, NY."
  />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>

<body class="home">
  <!-- AGE GATE OVERLAY -->
  <div id="age-gate" style="
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(0,0,0,0.97), rgba(0,0,0,1));
      z-index: 9999;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    ">
    <div style="
        max-width: 420px;
        width: 90%;
        padding: 2rem 2.2rem;
        background: #050509;
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(245,183,66,0.65);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.95);
        text-align: center;
      ">
      <h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">
        Adults Only – 18+
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #d3d3e6; margin-bottom: 1.1rem;">
        This site contains information related to the production of adult content.
        You must be at least 18 years old (or the legal age of majority in your region)
        to enter. If you are underage, you must leave now.
      </p>

      <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button id="age-yes" type="button" class="btn primary">
          I am 18 or older
        </button>
        <button id="age-no" type="button" class="btn secondary">
          I am under 18
        </button>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:0.9rem; font-size:0.8rem; color:#9b9bb5;">
        By clicking "I am 18 or older" you confirm that you are legally permitted
        to view and work with adult content in your jurisdiction.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="site-header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="brand-link">
        <span class="brand-mark">
          <img src="/img/lumennyx-mark.png" alt="LumenNyx sun/moon logo" />
        </span>
        <span class="brand-text">LUMENNYX STUDIOS</span>
      </a>

      <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="/model/profile">Model Portal</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
        <a href="/2257">2257</a>

        <% if (currentUser) { %>
          <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="/login">Portal Login</a>
        <% } %>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 2.5rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-logo-bg"></div>

      <h2>Independent Adult Production Studio</h2>
      <p>
        LumenNyx Studios is a small, independent adult content studio based near
        Wallkill, NY (Hudson Valley region). Our focus is clear communication,
        informed consent, and respectful, collaborative shoots with every
        performer.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/login" class="btn primary">Model / Staff Login</a>
        <a href="/register" class="btn secondary">Request Portal Access</a>
      </div>

      <p class="hero-note">
        This site is a private portal for models and approved collaborators.
        It is not a public video platform.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>How the Portal Works</h3>
      <p>The LumenNyx portal is where models and studio collaborators can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Maintain accurate legal identity and contact details.</li>
        <li>Upload ID, W-9, and other compliance documents securely.</li>
        <li>Review and sign a general / master model release.</li>
        <li>Set and update safety, consent, and hard/soft limits.</li>
        <li>Share headshots or portfolio photos for internal casting.</li>
        <li>View a record of scenes they have appeared in with the studio.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="field-help" style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
        All information in this portal is used for record-keeping, scheduling,
        and safety planning. It is not shared publicly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Legal & Compliance Overview</h3>
      <p>
        LumenNyx Studios follows U.S. federal record-keeping requirements for
        adult content (18 U.S.C. §2257 & related regulations) and maintains
        internal policies for performer safety and consent.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Every performer must be at least 18 years old on the date of any shoot and provide valid government ID.</li>
        <li>We keep signed model releases and ID records in a secure, non-public system for legal compliance.</li>
        <li>Performers can stop or change a scene at any time using clear stop-words or signals.</li>
        <li>Performers should review all paperwork and ask questions before signing anything.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="field-help" style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
        This site and its forms are for record-keeping and clarity only and are
        not individualized legal advice.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Model applications / portal access:</strong> models@lumennyxstudios.com</li>
        <li><strong>Support:</strong> support@lumennyxstudios.com</li>
        <li><strong>Billing:</strong> billing@lumennyxstudios.com</li>
        <li><strong>Releases / takedown requests:</strong> release@lumennyxstudios.com</li>
        <li><strong>2257 compliance:</strong> 2257@lumennyxstudios.com</li>
        <li><strong>Legal notices:</strong> legal@lumennyxstudios.com</li>
        <li><strong>General:</strong> contact@lumennyxstudios.com</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    (function () {
      var gate = document.getElementById('age-gate');
      if (!gate) return;

      var accepted = localStorage.getItem('lnx_age_ok');
      if (accepted === 'yes') {
        gate.style.display = 'none';
        return;
      }

      var yesBtn = document.getElementById('age-yes');
      var noBtn = document.getElementById('age-no');

      if (yesBtn) {
        yesBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
          localStorage.setItem('lnx_age_ok', 'yes');
          gate.style.display = 'none';
        });
      }

      if (noBtn) {
        noBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
          window.location.href = 'https://www.google.com';
        });
      }
    })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
